rComments: Sometimes, the professor went off to say something not important, its a bit hard to catch the main topic of what he is trying to say. And sometimes, there are also some strange phrases appear in the lecture, which is something should appear in a literature course. The form is not very appropriate. Its hard.
Vague grading criteria. You might wanna figure out the exact format of proof they want you to use in the course. Every problem set score is a surprise:)

Good lectures and examples, not as great handwriting haha. Practicals are hugely important to get in necessary practice. Make sure you understand each concept thoroughly as its easy to fall behind in understanding everything.
